pageContext.title: Digital Humanities 2009
pageContext.description_excerpt: Digital Humanities 2009-the annual joint meeting of the Association for Computers and the Humanities, the Association for Literary and Linguistic Computing, and the Society for Digital Humanities / Société pour l’étude des médias interactifs-was hosted by the Maryland Institute for Technology in the Humanities (MITH) at the University of Maryland in College Park.
pageContext.participants: Allen Renear, Claire Warwick, Jan Rybicki, John Nerbonne, Matthew Kirschenbaum, Michael Eberle-Sinatra, Neil Fraistat, Paul Spence, Stéfan Sinclair, Willard McCarty, Brett Barney
